content.rendered:
Directed by Jihyeon Jeong. Seung Ho Kim.

Written by Kwon Do-eun.

Cast Kim Ji-yeon( Ko Yu-rim 1) . Choi Hyun-wook( Moon Ji-woong 1) . Lee Joo-myung( Ji Seung-wan 1) . Seo Jae-hee( Shin Jae-kyung 1) . Kim Tae-ri( Na Hee-do 1) . Choi Myung-bin( Kim Min-chae 1) . Victoria Grace( Ko Yu-Rim 1) . Anzu Lawson( Hee-Doh 1) . Kim Hye-Eun( Coach Yang Chan-Mi 1) . Vivian Lu( Lee Da-Seul 1) . Kate Marley( Ji Seung-Wan 1) . Esther K. Chae( Shin Jae-Kyung 1) . Jully Lee( Coach Yang Chan-Mi 1) . Sanyee Yuan( Ye-Ji 1) . Mia Akemi Brown( Kim Min-Chae 1) . Bobby Foley( Jung-Hyuk 1) . Halley Kim( Jeong-Hyeon). Hao Feng( Jong-Chan). Aaron Yamawaki( Ko Yu-Rim’s Father). Raechel Wong( Ji Seung-wan’s mother). Garrison Michael Farquharson-Keener( Allen Smith – Referee). Christian Banas( Jung Ho-Jin). Kym Miller( Sophia Choi). Dawn Anderson( Jung Da Yeong)

Language Korean.

Producers Kim Beomrae. Seok Won Heo. Sun Tae Kim. Heon Ju Park. Series Sound Department. Mirage Zamprioli. Steven Lim. Matan Kaufman. Airi Mori. Series Visual Effects by. Jinhee Kim. Sanghwa Lee. Sung-min Alvin Yun.

Production Hwa and Dam Pictures. Studio Dragon.

 

Number of Seasons 1

Number of Episodes 16

Status Finished (2022–2022)
